{"tid":1431991,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[一齊入黎］大家有咩想同前線講","createTime":"2019-08-08T06:23:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T15:59:57.000Z","uid":77033,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"aa6570f03707d2c6416598749180459ae541e61d","tid":1431991,"uid":77033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:23:36.000Z","msg":"由於睇到之前好多示威人士被捕<br />\n黎緊又有示威活動 <br />\n想襯宜家提醒下各位<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好落單 唔好落單 唔好落單</span><br />\n好重要 講3次<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好戀戰</span> <br />\n撚完狗就好走 <br />\n暴動坐10年 唔值得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實每次遊行集會都會搞到一堆舖頭做唔到生意<br />\n冇生意 冇旅客 經濟差 <br />\n我覺得已經好成功<br />\n試下用經濟迫政府屈服<br />\n<br />\n盡量一班人活動 搵信得過既人幫手收風散出去<br />\n我知你地唔得閒成日上連登收風<br />\n<br />\n有前線分享過有鬼/on 9仔<br />\n明明得返好少人都話要死守<br />\n唔該你地<span style=\"color: red;\">保持頭腦清醒</span><br />\n唔好聽人講兩講就留低 <br />\n自己分析下<br />\n<br />\n速龍最近幾次拉人都係慢慢推進到得返幾百米就一野衝出黎禁低人<br />\n示威者人多 而且由早玩到晚 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">示威者散既速度一定唔夠班速龍快<br />\n所以唔好再死守佢黎你地咪走囉 </span><br />\n等佢地成班毅進仔拆路障唔好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你守住個街口有咩用姐？<br />\n做咩要企定定送頭姐？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲有 成日睇live 都見到有人口罩都冇個<br />\n係咪傻咖？<br />\n有d可能真係冇諗住參與 但最後參與左 而又俾記者影到直播出黎<br />\n所以唔該你地保護好自己！！！ <br />\n如果唔係警察秋後算帳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後歡迎其他手足補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc53d7b9165580206beaecb76044503efe1c94a1","tid":1431991,"uid":77033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:23:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f982295defd756258f8c9c7db9d68ad4eb5a1483","tid":1431991,"uid":55974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:24:51.000Z","msg":"唔好屌路人，路人會係你日後身邊既戰友黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09250fa705f7ac557064e87e08be9c2267eb4ec4","tid":1431991,"uid":282494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:26:05.000Z","msg":"保持道路暢通"},{"pid":"43de2c0e103bc8bba669a366ec354a7ce8851635","tid":1431991,"uid":270871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:33:24.000Z","msg":"感激不盡，無以為報"},{"pid":"41cfa3feba8f519995834e204fd542836063113e","tid":1431991,"uid":77033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:01:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"883d950d6c0d860074ac55005b7a02db62796a46","tid":1431991,"uid":77033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:02:17.000Z","msg":"推到有前線睇"},{"pid":"8e87994ec0518bc6e8332e52af4ad09c9cffbe3e","tid":1431991,"uid":77033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:02:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a0497356503a91a476c21f3195d10a70aeab17cb","tid":1431991,"uid":77033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:31:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5315d0c3f605075234508798e5ba21c95f5930da","tid":1431991,"uid":299510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:39:59.000Z","msg":"我反而覺得中後排真係要留後路比前線散<br />\n次次怕人踩人而散唔切就比中後排累死"},{"pid":"3ffb61628d9b4208b3bb4f47c72f0f53c1860110","tid":1431991,"uid":77033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:52:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3013988c94ca5fa3960f69256bd0175dbf5db3f","tid":1431991,"uid":77033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T14:20:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39a6b65864210c8f8174b2854d0dd02b5b16e7e9","tid":1431991,"uid":277541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:59:57.000Z","msg":"唔好企太迫，時刻留意逃生路線"}]}